
<acqabr>GENOVA</acqabr> {<acqcode>GNVA</acqcode>} SIGNS DEFINITIVE MERGER AGREEMENT
    DAVISON, Mich., March 25 - <acquired>Genova Inc</acquired> said it signed a
<status>definitive agreement</status> for the previously announced merger with
{<purchaser>Genova Products Inc</purchaser>}.
    Under the agreement, <purchabr>Genova Products</purchabr> will pay 5-3/8 dlrs a
share for the 29 pct of <acqabr>Genova</acqabr>'s outstanding common shares it
does not already own.
    The company said it plans to complete the transaction,
which requires shareholder approval, by the end of March.
